95+/-0.33}. Based on the X-ray emission, there is no evidence for a\nbreak in the main sequence at high stellar masses, although we cannot rule out\na turnover given the uncertainties in the scaling of L_X to SFR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2016 21:00:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2016 22:45:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-25"}
