ve that this symmetry is broken except\nwhen a combination of Dirichlet conditions in the even sector and a particular\nRobin condition in the odd sector is enforced, or viceversa, and that only the\nfirst of these two choices leads to a stable dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2016 22:19:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2017 15:55:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 Oct 2017 21:13:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-22"}
