as provide now with two\npossible ways of expressing the same perturbed quantities in terms of the\noriginal ones, one using only the nonperturbed biorthogonal family of Laurent\npolynomials, and the other using the Christoffel--Darboux kernel and its mixed\nversions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2016 00:09:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-14"}
