l then use this results to investigate the logical\nproperties of systems related to the principle, and introduce a proof\ntransformation technique to interpret constructively some non-constructive\nproofs of arithmetic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2016 14:23:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Dec 2016 13:23:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-28"}
