ape variations. This extension involves the use of local shape\npriors on object parts and provides robustness to limitations in shape training\ndata size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2016 15:37:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-14"}
